high_descs: Turn right then right again and walk towards the red microwave.
Open cabinet above red microwave and take out mug and close the cabinet.
Face the red microwave below you.
Open the red microwave, put the mug inside the red microwave and close it, open the red microwave, take out the mug and close the microwave again.
Turn around and face the counter on your right.
Place the mug in the coffee maker on the counter in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm mug in the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the far left corner of the kitchen and face the microwave.
Take the white mug out of the left cabinet above the microwave.
Lower the mug to countertop level.
Heat the empty mug in the microwave and take it out, then close the microwave door.
Turn around and go toward the coffee maker that was behind you.
Place the mug under the spout of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Set a heated mug on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around and walk up to the microwave on the kitchen counter
Open the left most cabinet above the microwave and remove the mug
Face down to look at the microwave
Heat the mug in the microwave then remove it
Turn around and approach the coffee maker behind you
Put the mug in the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put the mug in the coffee maker
